---
title: Glazed Teriyaki Chicken with Baby Bok Choy and Coconut Brown Rice
description: The sweet and savory combination of soy, honey, ginger, and garlic makes for a delicious glaze over juicy chicken and bok choy. Infused with rich and slightly sweet coconut milk, this is brown rice like you’ve never had it.
